Come on a musical journey with Toddler Rockers  where your little rockstars, aged 18 months to 3 years, discover a world of sounds and beats! In this playful program, we dive into the realm of tuned instruments such as Boomwhackers, Bells, Ukuleles, and more musical wonders. Whether your tiny tykes want to jam alongside Mum or Dad or groove solo in the center of our musical circle, our goal is to create a space bursting with excitement and comfort for them to explore.
